7
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,240
in the book.

8
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:18,480
It goes like this.

9
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:21,480
Because there is a law like gravity,

10
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:25,480
the universe can and will create itself from nothing.

11
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:28,800
And that was the reason he gave for saying we don't need God.

12
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,760
But just think of the statement.

13
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:33,600
Because there is a law like gravity,

14
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,960
that is because there is something.

15
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:38,120
The universe will create itself from nothing.

16
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:40,320
That's a flat contradiction before you start.

17
