20
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,960
Welcome to Westminster Chapel.

21
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:58,320
And to what I'm sure will be a really, really interesting

22
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:01,960
conference this evening, the Practical Wisdom Conference.

23
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,880
We're talking, of course, this evening

24
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:07,200
about faith in the age of science.

25
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:11,680
Very often in our era, many people, especially atheists,

26
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:15,080
have claimed that science effectively disproves God.

27
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:17,320
Well, someone who has been answering those atheists

28
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:21,040
