1844
01:31:54,700 --> 01:31:58,800
So we need to be very careful that we first recognize

1845
01:31:58,800 --> 01:32:02,000
that the people we're talking about are made

1846
01:32:02,000 --> 01:32:04,160
in the image of God and therefore,

1847
01:32:04,160 --> 01:32:06,760
as creatures of God have infinite value.

1848
01:32:06,880 --> 01:32:11,720
Once we've said that, we can now come to the next question

1849
01:32:11,720 --> 01:32:13,600
