1858
01:32:42,600 --> 01:32:46,820
Yeshua, as the Jews call him.

1859
01:32:46,820 --> 01:32:51,500
My Jewish friends believe that he died and didn't rise.

1860
01:32:52,480 --> 01:32:55,180
My Muslim friends believe he didn't die.

1861
01:32:57,120 --> 01:32:58,920
I believe he died and rose.

1862
