1888
01:34:16,760 --> 01:34:20,760
some sort of initiation that puts you on a path.

1889
01:34:20,760 --> 01:34:23,920
And I usually draw a wavy line ups and downs.

1890
01:34:23,920 --> 01:34:26,720
And you stay on the path, the sick full path

1891
01:34:26,720 --> 01:34:29,600
or whatever it is, the way, et cetera.

1892
01:34:29,600 --> 01:34:31,680
And you've got various people to help you,

1893
01:34:31,680 --> 01:34:35,160
priests, gurus, imams, all the rest of it.

1894
01:34:35,160 --> 01:34:39,040
And then you come to a gate at the end,

1895
01:34:39,040 --> 01:34:42,120
where I draw some scales of justice.

1896
01:34:42,120 --> 01:34:46,120
And at the end, you're faced with an assessment

1897
01:34:46,120 --> 01:34:50,280
of your behavior and your deeds up to that point.

1898
01:34:50,280 --> 01:34:54,160
And if you pass the grade, you get accepted

1899
01:34:54,160 --> 01:34:58,560
into whatever it is, nirvana, heaven, or whatever.

1900
01:34:58,560 --> 01:35:02,440
And most people will tell me that is what we believe.

1901
01:35:02,440 --> 01:35:05,000
And I say, perhaps the best way to think about it

1902
01:35:05,000 --> 01:35:07,520
is like a university course.

1903
01:35:07,520 --> 01:35:12,360
You have an entrance and then you study at the university,

1904
01:35:12,360 --> 01:35:13,800
every university in Britain

1905
01:35:13,800 --> 01:35:15,580
and around the world works this way.

1906
01:35:15,580 --> 01:35:18,320
The professors may be the best in the world,

1907
01:35:18,320 --> 01:35:21,400
but they cannot guarantee you a degree.

1908
01:35:21,400 --> 01:35:22,240
Why?

1909
01:35:22,240 --> 01:35:25,520
Because the whole principle of universities

1910
01:35:25,520 --> 01:35:29,320
is you get a degree on the basis of your merit.

1911
01:35:29,320 --> 01:35:33,800
And if you don't earn it, merit it, you don't get it, yes?

1912
01:35:33,800 --> 01:35:36,080
And many people say, yes, that is religion.

1913
01:35:36,080 --> 01:35:38,860
I've been told that by hundreds of people.

1914
01:35:38,860 --> 01:35:41,880
Well, I said, you see, that isn't Christianity.

1915
01:35:41,880 --> 01:35:43,880
And they say, oh, yes, it is.

1916
01:35:43,880 --> 01:35:46,000
Now, here's where the problem lies.

1917
01:35:46,000 --> 01:35:50,560
Many people think that Christianity is like that.

1918
01:35:50,560 --> 01:35:54,600
You pile up your good deeds, you try and please God,

1919
01:35:54,600 --> 01:35:58,320
and you hope at the end that he won't take his law too seriously

1920
01:35:58,320 --> 01:36:00,960
and will let you in.

1921
01:36:00,960 --> 01:36:03,880
But you see, it's not like that, folks.

1922
01:36:03,880 --> 01:36:07,920
Christianity, the acceptance is not

1923
01:36:07,920 --> 01:36:12,160
at the end of the journey of the judgment.

1924
01:36:12,160 --> 01:36:16,720
It's at the beginning of the journey at the cross.

1925
01:36:16,720 --> 01:36:19,160
Now, this is utterly revolutionary.

1926
01:36:19,160 --> 01:36:26,000
In that sense, Christianity is not a religion.

1927
01:36:26,000 --> 01:36:28,280
It isn't.

1928
01:36:28,280 --> 01:36:31,560
