So I came along, and I gave her a lovely present.

1946
01:37:34,640 --> 01:37:36,600
It was wrapped up, and I said, Sally,

1947
01:37:36,600 --> 01:37:39,360
I'd like you to be my wife.

1948
01:37:39,360 --> 01:37:40,480
Now, here's the present.

1949
01:37:40,480 --> 01:37:44,000
So she opened it, and it was a cookbook.

1950
01:37:44,000 --> 01:37:50,520
So I said, read page 153.

1951
01:37:50,520 --> 01:37:52,240
Apple cake.

1952
01:37:52,240 --> 01:37:54,640
Thou shall take so much flour.

1953
01:37:54,640 --> 01:37:56,600
Thou shall take so much sugar.

1954
01:37:56,600 --> 01:37:59,880
Thou shall put it in the oven and bake it, and so on.

1955
01:37:59,880 --> 01:38:05,040
Now, I said, my dear, I would like you to take this book.

1956
01:38:05,040 --> 01:38:07,560
And if you keep these rules, let's say,

1957
01:38:07,560 --> 01:38:11,840
