1958
01:38:11,840 --> 01:38:15,800
then I will accept you.

1959
01:38:15,800 --> 01:38:19,840
Otherwise, you can go back to your mother.

1960
01:38:19,840 --> 01:38:23,240
Why are you laughing, folks?

1961
